---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Jimmy Liu">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-link dark:text-link-dark">About</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-light-text dark:text-dark-text">
      <p>
        I am a purpose-driven Technical Program Manager at NVIDIA, where I
        orchestrate global data operations to fuel world-class ADAS and
        autonomous driving systems. My work focuses on building the underlying
        data loops and infrastructure that enable safety-critical technology,
        including delivery pipelines that have successfully powered NCAP 5-star
        safety ratings and L2++ autonomy.
      </p>

      <p>
        My journey into tech began with a Bachelor's in Biological Sciences from
        UC Santa Barbara. I pivoted into data and operations by leaning into my
        passion for problem-solving in ambiguous environments. Over the years,
        I've scaled data collection efforts at Amazon and Magic Leap, always
        looking for ways to automate the mundane and provide clarity through
        data visualization.
      </p>

      <p>
        I'm a builder at heart. Whether it's writing Python scripts to cut
        dataset release times by 70% or designing dashboards to track
        operational efficiency across continents, I thrive on creating tools
        that empower engineers and operations teams to do their best work.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-link dark:text-link-dark">
        Skills
      </h2>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 pb-8">
        <li class="pl-2 border-l-2 border-black dark:border-white">
          ML Operations (MLOps)
        </li>
        <li class="pl-2 border-l-2 border-black dark:border-white">
          Data Lifecycle Management
        </li>
        <li class="pl-2 border-l-2 border-black dark:border-white">
          Python & SQL Automation
        </li>
        <li class="pl-2 border-l-2 border-black dark:border-white">
          ADAS / AV Infrastructure
        </li>
        <li class="pl-2 border-l-2 border-black dark:border-white">
          Agile & Scrum Methodologies
        </li>
        <li class="pl-2 border-l-2 border-black dark:border-white">
          Regulatory Standards (NCAP)
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-link dark:text-link-dark">
        Experience Highlights
      </h2>
      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li class="pl-4 border-l-4 border-black dark:border-white">
          <span class="text-sm opacity-70">2024 — PRESENT</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-1">
            Technical Program Manager, ML Operations
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold opacity-80 mb-2">NVIDIA</p>
          <p class="text-sm">
            Led end-to-end data delivery for Active Safety features,
            contributing to NCAP 5-star ratings on upcoming Mercedes-Benz MMA
            platforms. Improved labeling output quality from 30% to 90% via
            iterative process refinements.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="pl-4 border-l-4 border-black dark:border-white">
          <span class="text-sm opacity-70">2022 — 2024</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-1">
            Technical Program Manager, AV Data Operations
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold opacity-80 mb-2">NVIDIA</p>
          <p class="text-sm">
            Managed global delivery of 13,000+ hours of driving data.
            Implemented P50/P90 uptime targets, yielding a 10% improvement in
            data output and reducing downtime by 30%.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="pl-4 border-l-4 border-black dark:border-white">
          <span class="text-sm opacity-70">2021 — 2022</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-1">
            Senior Data Collection Engineer
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold opacity-80 mb-2">Magic Leap</p>
          <p class="text-sm">
            Re-developed data collection pipelines for new workstreams,
            improving efficiency by 40%. Developed custom Python applications
            for hardware configuration and automated data tagging.
          </p>
        </li>

        <li class="pl-4 border-l-4 border-black dark:border-white">
          <span class="text-sm opacity-70">2020 — 2021</span>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-1">Data Collection Specialist</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold opacity-80 mb-2">Amazon Lab 126</p>
          <p class="text-sm">
            Led managed collection efforts for Alexa Q&A projects. Built
            SQL-based automated tagging workflows that increased delivery speed
            by 30%.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-link dark:text-link-dark">
        Education
      </h2>
      <div class="pl-4 border-l-4 border-black dark:border-white">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">B.S. in Biological Sciences</h3>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-80">
          University of California, Santa Barbara (2018)
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
